column3: “Absolutely the best sleep aid EVER!  Beautiful, stony, happy high, followed by deep, restful sleep.  Great dreams too.”
“Looks great as a lot but good and I think the name inspred me to get this 1  :-D”
“Love this strain before bed. love what this plant can do”
“Sounds like nice one for me and my significant other to use to make me relaxed.”
“just got it here. so far really nice headbandish right around the eyes high. great looking smells awesome.”
“If you are on a budget it will do. Unique taste (not so pleasant), pleasant body and mind effects.”
“Excellent strain good for sleeping or relaxing pretty strong and doesn't make me anxious like some other strains 4 1/2 to 5 stars for sure”
“Love it. Very sweet smell. Was having a very anxious day and this did the trick. Will be getting it again.”
“Had.opportunity to try this before bed and it was perfect.”
“Sounds like nice one to try with me and my significant other to get me relaxed and reduce my pain so I can be aroused.”

“4/5. Picked up a quarter from Rocky Road Dispensary in Avon, CO. The high hit me fairly quick, and i noticed amazing pain relief in my lower back and shoulders. Made me wanna lay down and listen to music. I couldn't help but smile and relax. Indica dominant, but you can feel some classic sativa effects. Very nice strain.”
